{"tid":2029894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人會叫 五大訴求？ 香港獨立唔講得？","createTime":"2020-05-22T12:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T03:22:24.000Z","uid":10788,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac116a7e6e3a6caeb4b6cfe9d7f3f373a9938272","tid":2029894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"人權法未過 獨立意志唔講得 要暗地裡做 而家已經2020年5月尾 人權法？ 毛都無條 中共已經唔理國際點睇  全世界都知中共仆街 你知我知單眼佬都知 <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問仲有冇人會叫 五大訴求？？ 問中共R真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？要睇國際線 唔講得？ 嘩 你咁白痴講到出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路 我哋需要一個口號統一我哋既意志 <br />\n<br />\n以下口號叫左十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9EZwqZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9EZwqZ.png&h=9312fcbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北美13殖民地被英國殖民12x年 因為英法百年戰爭 要加稅 殖民地人反抗  走上獨立道路 ,btw殖民地人同英國 係同文同種同制度（君主制）呢兩個地方差距細過 支那同香港好多  如今國安法要黎  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzXz4OJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzXz4OJ.png&h=9079bf60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"a1c63a545d0556701cb863e44187047bbee5181c","tid":2029894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"[有槍無敵？] 假如我坐時光機，番到當年既龍和道，放低一箱火魔，會唔會有人攞黎用？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好文一篇 重點係 香港人有無獨立既意志 參政既人有冇執政意志"},{"pid":"d70ddbee1417c7e0fc0110483d8fb867d493be64","tid":2029894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\